cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.LG 

This paper deals with tweet clustering for event detection, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also incorporates temporal information, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper involves probabilistic arguments, which could place it in cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
